@host = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### Health check (process alive)
GET {{host}}/healthz HTTP/1.1

### Readiness check (llama-server + qdrant reachable)
GET {{host}}/readyz HTTP/1.1

### Ingest a document (multipart file upload)
POST {{host}}/v1/ingest HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ingestBoundary

--ingestBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Rust is a systems programming language focused on safety, speed, and concurrency.
It achieves memory safety without a garbage collector via its ownership system.
--ingestBoundary--

### RAG query
POST {{host}}/v1/rag/query HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is Rust known for?"
}

### Classify text
POST {{host}}/v1/classify HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "The invoice total is $532.10 and is due on 2026-08-01.",
  "labels": ["invoice", "resume", "contract", "email"]
}

### Extract structured data
POST {{host}}/v1/extract HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Invoice #4471, total $532.10, due 2026-08-01, billed to Acme Corp.",
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "invoice_number": { "type": "string" },
      "total": { "type": "number" },
      "due_date": { "type": "string" },
      "customer": { "type": "string" }
    },
    "required": ["invoice_number", "total", "due_date", "customer"]
  }
}

### Route: classify path (labels provided)
POST {{host}}/v1/route HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "The invoice total is $532.10 and is due on 2026-08-01.",
  "labels": ["invoice", "resume", "contract", "email"]
}

### Route: extract path (schema provided)
POST {{host}}/v1/route HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Invoice #4471, total $532.10, due 2026-08-01, billed to Acme Corp.",
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "invoice_number": { "type": "string" },
      "total": { "type": "number" },
      "due_date": { "type": "string" },
      "customer": { "type": "string" }
    },
    "required": ["invoice_number", "total", "due_date", "customer"]
  }
}

### Route: RAG fallback path (no labels/schema)
POST {{host}}/v1/route HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "What is Rust known for?"
}
